{
  "id": "adv_bond_ktn_01_05",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "（うーん、次のお仕事まで時間が空いちゃったけど）\n（何してようかな……。本でも読む……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hmm‚ I have some free time until my next job.）\n（What should I do… Read a book…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.3544220607
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、こういう時に買った本って、結局その後）\n（読まないのよね。沙季のおすすめの本も読めてないし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But books bought at times like this usually end up）\n（unread. I haven't even finished the book Saki recommended.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3544220607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "（まぁ、このまま音楽を聴いて……）\n（…………あ、そうだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Well‚ I'll just keep listening to music like this…）\n（……Oh‚ right.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8215196927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "Sharing　想像以上の共鳴にFeeling\n光った～……♪",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sharing‚ resonating beyond imagination‚ Feeling\nShined~…♪",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0812257449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "（あ～～！　昨日作ったお姉ちゃんのプレイリスト）\n（すっっっっごくいい！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah~~! The playlist of my sister I made yesterday）\n（is soooOOOOO good!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1154437701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "（選曲はもちろん、曲の順番までこだわったし）\n（もちろん最後の曲は、『Gemstones』……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I put so much effort into the song selection and the order）\n（And of course‚ the last song is \"Gemstones\"…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9195710181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "（そうだ、いっそ全部ライブバージョンにして）\n（私だけのオリジナルライブを作るとか……！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Right‚ maybe I should use all live versions）\n（to create my own original live show…!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4887092907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "（って、なんだか雫みたいになっちゃってる……）\n（でも……やっぱりお姉ちゃんの歌、大好きだな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wait‚ I'm starting to sound like Shizuku…）\n（But… I really do love my sister's singing after all…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2186410586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんとは違う道を選んで、自分なりに答えを）\n（見つけて。時間は掛かっちゃったけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I chose a different path from her and found）\n（my own answer. It took some time‚ but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0872797966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "（少しは胸を張れるようになって、改めて思う）\n（お姉ちゃんは、私の――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Now that I can stand a bit taller‚ I realize again.）\n（My sister is my――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3972772916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.557410558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃい！？　えっ、えっ、あ、mihoさん！？\nど、ど、ど、どうかしました！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek!? Oh‚ oh‚ miho-san!?\nI-I-Is something wrong!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.783741182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "ニヤニヤしながら、全身でリズムを刻んでいたら\nさすがに気になるでしょう。何を聴いていたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were grinning and bobbing to the rhythm with your whole body.）\nOf course it’s going to catch my eye. What were you listening to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1001814465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇぇ……わ、私、そんなことしてました……？\nえっと、曲は、その、mihoさんには…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh… I-I was doing that…?\nWell‚ the song is‚ um‚ to you‚ miho-san……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8952835977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "…………あぁ、長瀬麻奈ね\nそうならそうと言えばいいじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Ah‚ Nagase Mana‚ I see.\nIf that's it‚ you should just say so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7742630899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "っ……そう、ですけど\n嫌いな人に、わざわざ言うのもあれですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I mean‚ that's true‚ but\ntelling someone who dislikes her seemed a bit much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.200408103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……いくら嫌いでも、さすがにもう、家族の前で\n故人を貶めたりしないわ。悪かったと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No matter how much I dislike her‚ I wouldn't\nbadmouth the deceased anymore. I feel bad about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.077936834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "（……そっか。mihoさんも大切な人を亡くしてるん）\n（だっけ。意外と、共通点多いのかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…I see. miho-san also lost someone precious‚）\n（didn't she. We might have more in common than I thought…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8623811979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "（大切な人を亡くして、時に道を間違えて、後悔して）\n（それでも前に進もうとしてる。だからあの時も……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Losing someone dear‚ losing one's way at times‚ regretting it.）\n（Yet still trying to move forward. Is that why‚ back then too…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8151022533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "何？　それとも、名前を出したくらいで暴れるような\n器の小さい人間だとでも思われてるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Or do you think I'm such a narrow-minded person\nthat I'd lose my temper just at the mention of her name?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.9772112786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ！　そんなことないです、けど……\nmihoさんって、結構いい人ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no! It's not that‚ but…\nmiho-san‚ you're actually a pretty good person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4533090213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "常識があるだけで『いい人』なんて言われたくないわ\n大人なら、あって当然……いえ、そんなことないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to be called a \"good person\" just for having common sense.\nIt should be natural for an adult… No‚ wait‚ that's not always true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.6485975204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_05-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……なんで言い直したんでしょう……\nもしかしてfranさんとkanaさんのことかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-Ahaha… why did she correct herself…\nCould it be because of fran and kana…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.1101222294,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}